    "path": "/React JS/2022-03-01 Vanila vs React2/",
    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2>Vanila로 만든 클릭시 숫자가 변하는 부분을 React로 구현해보자</h2>\n<p>좋은 방법과 좋지않는 방법이 있는데 좋지 않는 방법부터 알아보자</p>\n<h3>좋지 않은 방법(React)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Vanila JS</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'btn'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> span <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'span'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> counter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">클릭카운트증가</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  counter <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> counter <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n  span<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'총 클릭수 : '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> counter\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nbutton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 클릭카운트증가<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// React JS 좋지 않은 방법</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 변수를 JSX에 전달하는 방법 : {변수명}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">클릭카운트증가</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Container</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">총 클릭수 : </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>클릭카운트증가<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Container</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> root<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 이 코드는 제대로 작동되지 않음</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컴포넌트를 단 한번만 렌더링하기 때문에 counter는 증가하지만 UI가 업데이트(리렌더링) 되지 않아 반영되지 않음</p>\n<p>그러면 우리가 원하는대로 ReRender 시켜보자!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 클릭할때마다 함수가 실행되면서 새로 렌더링</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Rendering : 바꾸어 보여주는 작업</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">클릭카운트증가</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">렌더링</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">렌더링</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Container</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> root<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Container</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">총 클릭수 : </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\"> // 변수를 JSX에 전달하는 방법\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>클릭카운트증가<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">클릭해줘</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">렌더링</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>어플리케이션이 실행될 때 카운터는 0,</li>\n<li>ReactDOM이 Container를 root에 렌더링 시킨다 (카운터 : 0)</li>\n<li>root라는 빈 div안에 Container 컴포넌트의 내용물들이 추가되기 시작(span, button, 이벤트)</li>\n<li>버튼을 클릭하게 되면 클릭카운트증가 함수를 호출하게 되고 카운터를 증가 (카운터 : 1)</li>\n<li>그리고 렌더링 함수를 호출, Container가 다시 렌더링된다.(카운터 1이 화면에 보임)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Vanila --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 렌더링 --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 렌더링 --></span>\n    총 클릭수 :\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 렌더링 --></span>\n    카운트\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 렌더링 --></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- React --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      총 클릭수 : 카운트\n      <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 이곳만 렌더링 --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>클릭해줘<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>React.js는 이전에 렌더링된 컴포넌트를 알고 다음에 렌더링 될 컴포넌트에서 다른 부분만 파악한다</p>\n<h3>좋은 방법(React)</h3>\n<p>안좋은 방법에서는 데이터가 바뀔때마다 렌더링 함수를 호출하는 걸 잊어서는 안된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// React.js 어플 내에서 데이터를 보관하고 자동으로 리렌더링을 일으킬 수 있는 방법</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Container은 App으로 변경(관습)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'root'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// [0, 함수]</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 첫번째가 data, 두번째가 data를 변경할 때 사용하는 함수</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">총 클릭수 : </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>클릭카운트증가<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">클릭해줘</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">App</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> root<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 안좋은 방법</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// data 초기값</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">클릭카운트증가</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// data값을 변경하는 함수</span>\n  카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">렌더링</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 좋은 방법</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// [0, 함수]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> 카운터 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> 카운터수정 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 조금 더 깔끔하게 표현</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>카운터<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 카운터수정<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>State?</p>\n<p>state는 기본적으로 object이며, 컴퍼넌트 자신이 가지고 있는 속성 값</p>\n<p>간단히 말해 리렌더링을 통해 자주 변경될 것 같은 값을 변수가 아닌 state에 저장해서 관리함</p>\n<p>카운트 값(state)을 변경해보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 왜 변경함수를 사용해야 하는가?</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 카운트수정<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">클릭카운트증가</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">총 클릭수 : </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> 클릭카운트증가 <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">클릭해줘</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 카운트가 증가하나 리렌더링이 되지않아서 UI가 업데이트 되지않음</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">클릭카운트증가</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\tReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">App</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> root<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 리렌더링이 필요한 곳마다 넣어줘야함</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 이것 떄문에 변경함수가 존재</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 카운트수정<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 보통 state의 이름이 counter면 변경함수의 이름은 setCounter</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">클릭카운트증가</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">카운트수정</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 변경함수는 안에 들어있는 값으로 업데이트하고 리렌더링을 시켜준다</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 값을 바꾸고 리렌더링, 이 모든 것이 변경함수 안에서 일어난다</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">총 클릭수 : </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onClick</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> 클릭카운트증가 <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">클릭해줘</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\t</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>변경함수를 이용해서 state를 변경할 때마다 컴포넌트 전체가 새로운 값을 가지고 재생성된다.</p>\n<p>이때 전부 바뀌는 것이 아닌 변경되는 부분만 바뀌게 된다</p>\n<h3>변경함수 팁</h3>\n<p>변경함수로 값을 업데이트 할 때 state의 값을 직접적으로 사용하는 것은 좋은 방법이 아니다</p>\n<p>state의 값이 다른 곳에서도 변경될 수 있기 때문이다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 좋지 않은 방법</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 다른 곳에서 변경되어서 우리가 원하던 값이 아닐 수 있다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>카운트<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 카운트수정<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">클릭카운트증가</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">카운트수정</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> 카운트 <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 좋은 방법</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">클릭카운트증가</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 변경함수 안에 함수도 가능</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 첫번째 인자는 현재값</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">카운트수정</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">current</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> current <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 안전한 방법</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>현재의 state를 바탕으로 다음 state를 계산하고 싶다면 좋은 방법을 선택</p>\n<p>예상치 못한 업데이트가 일어나도 혼동을 주는걸 방지</p>\n<h2>Source</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>노마드 코더 리액트 강의</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://nomadcoders.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://nomadcoders.co/</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>리액트</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.reactjs.org/docs/faq-state.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ko.reactjs.org/docs/faq-state.html</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/React JS/2022-03-01 Vanila vs React2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Vanila JS vs React JS (State 편)","summary":"Vanila로 작성한 코드와 React로 작성한 코드 비교","date":"2022.03.01.","categories":["React","Javascript"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9ec1ce1fffcf86506708c068fff71fd9/f4073/js-main.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9ec